Survey of 101 divorce lawyers show the #1 reason for divorce is boredom, 7 out of 10 divorces initiated by women.
We need law reform. If a woman wants to leave because she is "bored" she can do without the alimony.
If a person has enough time to be bored maybe they are not contributing enough to the family?
